{
  "name": "XmlSchemas",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>XmlMap</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlMap/XmlMap .htm#XmlMap.Schemas\">Schemas</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>XmlSchemas</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlSchemas/XmlSchemas .htm#XmlSchemas.Item\">Item</a></strong> 方法可从 <strong>XmlSchemas</strong> 集合返回一个 <strong>XmlSchema</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一项XmlMap所包含的第二个XML架构的命名空间的前缀。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlSchemas = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Schemas</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xmlSchemas.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Namespace</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Prefix</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上第一项XmlMap所包含XML架构的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlSchemas = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Schemas</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`XML架构的数量：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${xmlSchemas.Count}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlMap/XmlMap .htm#XmlMap.XmlMap\">XmlMap</a></strong> 对象包含的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlSchema/XmlSchema .htm#XmlSchema.XmlSchema\">XmlSchema</a></strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一项XmlMap所包含XML架构的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlMap = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xmlMap.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Schemas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上第一项XmlMap所包含的第一个XML架构的内容赋值给A7单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlSchemas = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Schemas</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A7&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = xmlSchemas.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XML</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一项XmlMap所包含的第二个XML架构的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlSchemas = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Schemas</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xmlSchemas.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
